event_name: Songs of the Sea featuring Fergus O'Byrne and Jim Payne
location: Old City Arts Hub @ St Andrew's United Church, 315 Fitzwilliam Street Nanaimo, BC V9R 3A6
description: An evening of traditional maritime music with Fergus O'Byrne and Jim Payne. Special guests include Nanaimo-based Fiddelium, winners of the 2023 Canadian Folk Music award for young performers of the year.
